r","background-size":"auto","background-attachment":"scroll","background-type":"","background-media":"","overlay-type":"","overlay-color":"","overlay-opacity":"","overlay-gradient":""}},"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[6],"tags":[378,753,828,350,114,397,128,468,327,555],"class_list":["post-32714","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-wisdom-al-hikmah","tag-cure-al-dawa","tag-disease-al-daa","tag-healing-al-shafa","tag-health","tag-manners-adab","tag-medicine-al-tibb","tag-providence-al-qada-wal-qadr","tag-self-al-nafs","tag-sickness-al-marad","tag-spirit-ar-ruh"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8vE","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":5243,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/16\/tibb-every-disease-has-cure\/","url_meta":{"origin":32714,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Allah created a cure for every disease","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah did not send down any disease but that he also sent its cure.\" In another narration, the Prophet said, \"One who has knowledge of it knows it, and one ignorant of it is ignorant.\"\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17563,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/11\/best-thing-khuluq-hasan-adab\/","url_meta":{"origin":32714,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Good character best thing given by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 11, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Sharik reported: I witnessed bedouins ask the Prophet, saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the best thing a servant may be given?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGood character.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3436 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32706,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/all-cures-but-aging\/","url_meta":{"origin":32714,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Allah placed cures for all diseases, except aging","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Sharik reported: A bedouin said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, shall we not seek treatment?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYes, O servants of Allah, seek treatment. Verily, Allah did not place a disease but that he also placed its treatment or cure, except for one ailment.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8161,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/blackseed-cure-except-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":32714,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Healing properties of blackseed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"This blackseed is healing for all diseases but poison.\u201d She said, \u201cWhat is poison?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cDeath.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5363 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0627\u0626\u0634\u0629 \u0642\u0627\u0644\u062a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/24\/seek-healing-not-haram\/","url_meta":{"origin":32714,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Seek cure for disease from what is lawful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah sent down the disease and the cure, and for every disease He made a cure. Seek treatment, but do not seek treatment by the unlawful.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3874 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":771,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/10\/no-healing-but-you\/","url_meta":{"origin":32714,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Healing: Take away the pain by Your healing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 10, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would visit a sick person, he would say,\u00a0\u201cTake away the pain, O Lord of all people, and give healing for You are the Healer. There is no healing but Your healing, a healing that leaves no trace\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32714","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=32714"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32714\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=32714"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=32714"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=32714"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}